---
title: Breaded Ranch Chicken with Potato Coins and Green Beans
description: Everyone's favourite dip – ranch – plays double duty in this satisfying supper! It adds zing to a side of potatoes, and we've also snuck some under the breadcrumb topping for the chicken!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-pane-a-la-sauce-ranch-a67ba7cb.jpg
